snippet.title: Reacting to Johnny Depp speaking French
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp speaking French! In this video I am reacting to Johnny Depp speaking French. Reaction videos are always fun so I decided to make some more on my channel. It will be a great way for you to listen to some French and improve your listening  skills. #johnnydepp  #learnfrench #french #myfrenchstory

Watch the original video here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W145mu5_29k
